<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When calling createRow() from a Zend_Db_Table object that have a custom row class, it throws an exception, because Zend_Loader::loadClass is called unconditionally, no matter whether a custom __autoload was implemented. Same problem in Zend_Db_Table::fetchRow() and Zend_Db_Table_Rowset constructor.</p>

